        <mxCell id="ea-leg3" value="Isolation Rules:&#xa;1. No direct DB access across engine boundaries&#xa;2. All inter-engine comms via Event Bus only&#xa;3. Each engine owns its tables exclusively&#xa;4. Shared infra (Supabase, Redis, Apify, Claude) injected&#xa;5. Each engine has its own API namespace&#xa;6. Any engine extractable as standalone microservice" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
